Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,research associate Joe Savits give a\Nspecial shout-out to Jonathon Dunn,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank our surgeon admiral sam. Thanks Joe\Nand John, Thanks Sam! More information can
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,be found at pateron.com/HEALTHCARETRIAGE
